data.description: Escape to this charming mountain retreat that effortlessly blends comfort with outdoor living. Step onto the front deck and let the crisp mountain air soothe your soul, while the low maintenance Trex decking guarantees less upkeep and more time to soak in the serene surroundings. Inside, the kitchen and bathroom have been tastefully updated with sleek countertops and modern sinks, giving the home a fresh and stylish feel. Enjoy the energy efficiency and natural light flowing through the dual-pane vinyl windows, adding to the cozy ambiance. The loft area is a versatile space with two separate sleeping areas, perfect for hosting guests or creating a tranquil home office. Take advantage of the screened porch, providing a protected area for laundry and a peaceful spot to savor the outdoors without pesky insects. The fully fenced yard is a bonus feature, offering a secure space to entertain. Admire the lush fruit trees and tall pines, adding beauty and tranquility to the yard. With ample parking, including RV space, there's plenty of room to store your outdoor gear and vehicles. The additional storage and workbench in the crawl space below the house is a special added touch. Don't miss out on this mountain gem!
